text: Emily Warren (born 1992) is an American singer. Emily Warren may also refer to: * Emily Warren (artist) (1869–1956), artist and illustrator * Emily Warren (courtesan) (died 1780s), English courtesan * Emily Warren Roebling (1843–1903), helped complete the Brooklyn Bridge when her husband, Chief Engineer Washington Roebling, fell ill
title: Emily Warren (disambiguation)
